videos.description: Jacob Park connects with WR Allen Lazard in the corner of the end zone for a touchdown for the Cyclones.
videos.headline: Iowa State strikes first with TD

videos.description: Nathan Stanley throws a touchdown pass to Nick Easley for 10 yards to tie the game in the first quarter.
videos.headline: Easley's TD catch ties game

videos.description: Anthony Nelson and  A. J. Epenesa sack Jacob Park for a loss of 10 yards ending Iowa State's drive.
videos.headline: Iowa defense gets drive ending sack

videos.description: Iowa State's David Montgomery runs outside for a big gain in the second quarter.
videos.headline: Montgomery breaks off 36-yard run

videos.description: Nathan Stanley finds Matt VandeBerg who makes the  leaping catch in the end zone to give Iowa the lead.
videos.headline: Iowa takes lead on leaping TD catch

videos.description: Iowa head coach Kirk Ferentz says he is proud of his guys for the way they responded after trailing in the first half.
videos.headline: Ferentz happy with Iowa's resiliency in 1st half

videos.description: Iowa State head coach Matt Campbell says his team needs to have poise in order to regain the lead in the second half.
videos.headline: Campbell wants Iowa State to contain emotion in 2nd half

videos.description: Akrum Wadley soars over the defensive line into the end zone to extend the Hawkeyes' lead.
videos.headline: Wadley leaps for TD to widen Iowa's lead

videos.description: Iowa State's Jacob Park finds Allen Lazard in the end zone for a three-yard touchdown to cut the Hawkeyes' lead.
videos.headline: Lazard catches 2nd TD of the game for Cyclones

videos.description: T. J. Hockenson  makes a 17 yard catch and run but loses the ball on the one yard line.
videos.headline: T.J. Hockenson leaps for the pylon  but is called down at the 1-yard line

videos.description: Jacob Park finds Hakeem Butler down the field for a 30-yard touchdown to give the Cyclones the lead.
videos.headline: Park finds wide open WR for Iowa State TD

videos.description: David Montgomery breaks multiple tackles and pushes into the end zone for seven-yard touchdown to extend the Cyclones lead.
videos.headline: Montgomery breaks tackles and drives in for a Iowa St TD

videos.description: Ihmir Smith-Marsette dives for a 15-yard pass in the end zone for a Hawkeye touchdown in the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: Iowa creates close game with diving TD catch

videos.description: Parker Hesse intercepts Jacob Park's pass and returns it for 17 yards to give Iowa the ball in the red zone with 6 minutes left.
videos.headline: Hawkeyes get huge interception

videos.description: Jacob Parker throws it 74-yards to Hakeem Butler who was wide open to give the Cyclones the lead with less than 5 minutes to go.
videos.headline: Hakeem Butler hauls in 74-yard TD pass to give Iowa St the lead

videos.description: Akrum Wadley catches the ball and breaks off for a 46-yard run straight to the end zone to tie the game late.
videos.headline: Wadley rips off 46-yard TD to tie the game late in the 4th quarter

videos.description: Iowa's Nathan Stanley throws a five-yard pass Ihmir Smith-Marsette in the end zone to win the game in overtime.
videos.headline: Iowa wins game on 5 yard TD in overtime
